Overview of changes in lightdm 0.0.2

    * Improve build messages
    * Replace "eb expand" with "eb --expand"
    * Allow unversioned packages
    * Add intltool rules
    * Add man rules
    * Add gsettings rules
    * Add desktop rules
    * Add dpkg rules
    * Add PPA rules
    * Add RPM rules
    * Add --verbose option

